CALCULATOR

A basic C++ console line calculator made for the mac.

FEATURES
* Add functionality
* Subtract functionality
* Multiplication functionality
* Division functionality
* Loop through

HOW TO SETUP
* This is built for the mac, so, it needs Xcode
* Download the source code 
* Open the whole project by double clicking the .xcodeproj file
* On the left panel, you should see product
* If not, just run the project first by holding Command + R
* Click on the drop down beside the “Product” word
* Right click and click “Show In Finder”
* Drag the terminal app to anywhere you want it to be

Enjoy! 